# Cursor AI Rules for Gladly Conversation Analyzer

## Project Overview
- Flask backend with React frontend
- Docker-based deployment on AWS EC2
- HTTPS support with SSL certificates
- IAM roles for S3 access (no AWS credentials)

## Deployment Workflow
- Local development → Push to GitHub
- EC2: Pull from GitHub → Deploy with ./deploy.sh production
- Uses .env files for environment variables
- Infrastructure managed with Terraform

## Key Files
- deploy.sh - Main deployment script
- setup_https_infrastructure.sh - One-time HTTPS setup
- .env - Environment variables (on EC2)
- terraform/main.tf - Infrastructure config
